'''荒唐好萊塢'''（英語：Episodes）是英美合拍的電視[[情境喜劇|情境喜劇]]，由[[David_Crane_(writer/producer)|David Crane]]和[[Jeffrey_Klarik|Jeffrey Klarik]]編劇，並由[[Hat_Trick_Productions|Hat Trick Productions]]製作。<ref name="bbcprdec">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2010/12_december/17/episodes.shtml |title=Press Packs: Episodes |publisher=BBC |date=December 17, 2010 |accessdate=December 19, 2010 |archive-date=2013-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921101902/http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2010/12_december/17/episodes.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在2011年1月9日晚上9:30於[[Showtime電視網|Showtime]]電視台首播。<ref>[http://thefutoncritic.com/news/2010/09/22/biggest-sunday-ever-on-showtime-shameless-episodes-and-californication-to-premiere-january-9th-37549/20100922showtime02/ "Biggest Sunday Ever on Showtime! Shameless, Episodes & Californication to Premiere January 9th"] {{Wayback|url=http://thefutoncritic.com/news/2010/09/22/biggest-sunday-ever-on-showtime-shameless-episodes-and-californication-to-premiere-january-9th-37549/20100922showtime02/ |date=20200614012741 }}, Showtime [[press_release|press release]], September 22, 2010, via FutonCritic.com. Retrieved November 3, 2010.</ref> 並在2011年1月10日22時在[[BBC2台|BBC2台]]首播。<ref name="bbcprdec"/> 本劇描述英國的一對情境喜劇編劇夫妻搬到[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]重新創作他們在英國受歡迎的喜劇，結果卻引起災難性的後果。Showtime電視台和英國BBC電視台已經續約第二季。<ref>{{cite web|title=BBC Two orders more Episodes|url=http://www.atvtoday.co.uk/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=838:bbc-two-orders-more-episodes&catid=1:tv-media&Itemid=3|publisher=www.atvtoday.co.uk|accessdate=27 February 2011|archive-date=2012-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314210741/http://www.atvtoday.co.uk/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=838:bbc-two-orders-more-episodes&catid=1:tv-media&Itemid=3|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.comedy.co.uk/news/story/00000478/episodes_tamsin_greig_stephen_mangan_series_2/ |title=Second series of 9 episodes |accessdate=2012-01-23 |archive-date=2013-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130429102338/http://www.comedy.co.uk/news/story/00000478/episodes_tamsin_greig_stephen_mangan_series_2 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>本劇已經在全世界186個國家播送。<ref name="international">{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/broadcasting/news/a304146/episodes-sold-to-186-countries.html?rss |title='Episodes' sold to 186 countries |publisher=Digital Spy |date=February 16, 2011 |accessdate=March 2, 2011}}</ref>2015年6月，Showtime宣布續訂第五季，並於2016年於倫敦拍攝，全季共九集。

== 劇情概要 ==
