該劇在美國觀眾中評價相當多元。
*Robert Bianco在報紙[[今日美國|今日美國]]上評論本劇「輕易地當選本季最佳喜劇」<ref>{{cite news |title= Experience great 'Episodes' of laughter, thanks to LeBlanc |author= Robert Bianco |url= http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2011-01-07-episodes07_ST_N.htm |newspaper= USA Today |date= January 6, 2011 |accessdate= January 14, 2011 |archive-date= 2011-10-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20111011000833/http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2011-01-07-episodes07_ST_N.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>。
*[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]影評記者馬修·吉爾伯特（Matthew Gilbert）表示：“該季的每一集就像是每一個愉悅的小部分”。<ref>{{cite news |title= A clever satire about the travails of adaptation |author= Matthew Gilbert |url= http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2011/01/07/episodes_a_clever_adaptation_about_the_travails_of_adaptation/ |newspaper= Boston Globe |date= January 7, 2011 |accessdate= January 14, 2011 |archive-date= 2012-11-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20121102211927/http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2011/01/07/episodes_a_clever_adaptation_about_the_travails_of_adaptation/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>
*[[Boston_Herald|Boston Herald]]影評記者Mark A. Perigard則溫和地描述他擔心恐怕不會有太多觀眾欣賞。<ref>{{cite news |title= Big names, little roles |author= Mark A. Perigard |url= http://www.bostonherald.com/entertainment/television/reviews/view/20110106big_names_little_roles_its_showtime_sort_of_for_leblanc_and_macy/srvc=home&position=7 |newspaper= Boston Herald |date= January 6, 2011 |accessdate= January 14, 2011 |archive-date= 2012-10-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20121004181952/http://www.bostonherald.com/entertainment/television/reviews/view/20110106big_names_little_roles_its_showtime_sort_of_for_leblanc_and_macy/srvc%3Dhome%26position%3D7 |dead-url= no }}</ref>
